templates.name: show all careplan and related nodes for patient $firstname $familyname
templates.text: What are the components related to caring for patient $firstname $familyname?
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[rel1:CAREPLAN_INVOLVES_PATIENT]-(carePlan:CarePlan)
OPTIONAL MATCH (carePlan)-[otherRel]->(otherNode)
RETURN patient, rel1, carePlan, otherRel, otherNode

templates.name: show all AllergyIntolerance and Observation for patient  $firstname $familyname (Abbott Pok)
templates.text: What are the allergic symptoms of patient $firstname $familyname
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})-[:ALLERGYINTOLERANCE_AFFECTS_PATIENT]->(allergy:AllergyIntolerance)
OPTIONAL MATCH (allergy)-[:ALLERGY_ASSOCIATED_WITH_OBSERVATION]->(observation:Observation)
RETURN patient, allergy, observation

templates.name: show all immunization and related encounter for patient $firstname $familyname
templates.text: What vaccination records does patient $firstname $familyname have
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[administeredTo:IMMUNIZATION_ADMINISTERED_TO_PATIENT]-(immunization:Immunization)
OPTIONAL MATCH (immunization)-[administeredDuring:IMMUNIZATION_ADMINISTERED_DURING_ENCOUNTER]->(encounter:Encounter)
RETURN patient, administeredTo, immunization, administeredDuring, encounter

templates.name: show all medication request and medication for patient $firstname $familyname
templates.text: Show me the medication request and associated medication details for patient $firstname $familyname
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[prescribes:MEDICATIONREQUEST_PRESCRIBED_FOR_PATIENT]-(medicationRequest:MedicationRequest)
OPTIONAL MATCH (medicationRequest)-[generates:MEDIREQUEST_GENERATES_MEDICATION]->(medication:Medication)
RETURN patient, prescribes, medicationRequest, generates, medication

templates.name: show all information about obervation and encounter for patient $firstname $familyname
templates.text: What was patient $firstname $familyname last visit about?
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[encounterRel:ENCOUNTER_INVOLVES_PATIENT]-(encounter:Encounter)
OPTIONAL MATCH (encounter)<-[observationRel:OBSERVATION_RECORDED_DURING_ENCOUNTER]-(observation:Observation)
RETURN patient, encounterRel, encounter, observationRel, observation

templates.name: show all encounter information related to patient $firstname $familyname
templates.text: What medical records does patient $firstname $familyname have?
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[rel:ENCOUNTER_INVOLVES_PATIENT]-(encounter:Encounter)
RETURN patient, rel, encounter

templates.name: Show all diagnostic reports for patient  $firstname $familyname (Zackary Kozey)
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})<-[rel:DIAGREPORT_CONCERNS_PATIENT]-(report:DiagnosticReport)
RETURN patient, rel, report

templates.name: show all condition related to patient $firstname $familyname
templates.cypher:
MATCH (patient:Patient {firstname: $firstname, familyname: $familyname})
WITH patient
MATCH (condition:Condition)-[rel:CONDITION_RELATES_TO_PATIENT]->(patient)
RETURN patient, rel, condition
